@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = yushin@example.com
@password = Password123!
@dbQuery = 디스이즈네버댓 Regular Jeans Blue

### 1. Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
%}

### 2. Rebuild product search index
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/search-index/rebuild
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 3. Search products after index rebuild
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/search?q={{dbQuery}}&page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
